<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.10">
<l>tiṟalmurukaṉa ṉaiyārteṉ ṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>vaṟamutalva ṉavaṉai yaṇiyāliyar kōṉmaruvār</l>
<l>kaṟaineṭuvēl valavaṉ kalikaṉṟico laiyiraṇṭum</l>
<l>muṟaivaḻuvā maivallārmuḻu tāḷvarvā ṉulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master the two-times-five [verses], without error in the order,</l>
<l>Of Kalikaṉṟi, the one skilled with the long spear with enemy blood,</l>
<l rend="indent">king of those of lovely Āli,</l>
<l>About the source of virtue who stands eternally</l>
<l rend="indent">in Aḻuntai of the south where [dwell]</l>
<l>Those like valorous Murukaṉ, they will fully rule the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
